<Title>Alerting and Transponder Control Panel</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided tuning and control panels operate normally.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Use a TCP to perform alerting and transponder panel functions:</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Use the MENU key to access the ALERT/XPDR CTL on/off control and  ALERT/XPDR menu. </Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Use the XPDR menu to access the transponder IDENT function.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
